{"tid":1876039,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(反了反了) 疫情告急之際  北大教授貼文用崇禎影射皇上","createTime":"2020-02-12T06:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T02:12:17.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a3001fffe7bf526ceb1541364a155765a518f8f2","tid":1876039,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T06:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nRI9l3Jr7PjI9__8ZbXiZg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTU1Mi4zMDQxNDc0NjU0Mzc4/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/HalH9w8hOvemHPLZ3mknkw--~B/aD0zNDA7dz00MzQ7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/7720fe8431e0ad44477dc7654f81daa1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnRI9l3Jr7PjI9__8ZbXiZg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTU1Mi4zMDQxNDc0NjU0Mzc4%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHalH9w8hOvemHPLZ3mknkw--~B%2FaD0zNDA7dz00MzQ7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2F7720fe8431e0ad44477dc7654f81daa1&h=38577e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京大學中文系教授孔慶東 1 月 30 日在微博發文，裡頭意有所指地寫著，「大順軍的炮聲，已經轟響在宣武門了。朱老師站在太和殿前，最後搖了一遍上課鈴，一個學生也沒有來。老朱知道，該下課了。他收拾好講義，從神武門走出去，來回溜躂了兩圈，然後登上煤山，緩緩看了一陣自己天天講課的校園。滿天的烏雲都沈默著，等待覆蓋他最後一句，正在醞釀的留言。」<br />\n<br />\n崇禎皇帝是明朝的亡國帝，即位之時，大明江山已是外強中乾，再加上他用人不善，沒有足夠出色的政治才能，只會紙上談兵。而在個性方面，部份後世的史學家認為崇禎皇帝孤僻多疑、剛愎自用、獨斷專行的個性，也是造成明朝最後滅亡的原因。這位明朝的末代皇帝，最後就是在北京的煤山上自縊而亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wc_jIYqkKnbuTHq0ZC.WLA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD0xMjQy/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/5wpfVhSpffSAPOBfPR2KAA--~B/aD02NTA7dz02NTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.com/8de83cb8a71eb8c4ca84c4a34b097be1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fwc_jIYqkKnbuTHq0ZC.WLA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD0xMjQy%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5wpfVhSpffSAPOBfPR2KAA--~B%2FaD02NTA7dz02NTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.com%2F8de83cb8a71eb8c4ca84c4a34b097be1&h=0a3f90c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n按中共官方對言論的控管，孔慶東此番言論已接近造反，果然此文發表不久後，隨即遭到刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%9A%B1%E5%8C%BF%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E5%8C%97%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E7%94%A8%E5%B4%87%E7%A6%8E%E5%BD%B1%E5%B0%84%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-095844515.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%259A%25B1%25E5%258C%25BF%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585-%25E5%258C%2597%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2595%2599%25E6%258E%2588%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25B4%2587%25E7%25A6%258E%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-095844515.html&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GDJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=606b993e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%9A%B1%E5%8C%BF%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85-%E5%8C%97%E5%A4%A7%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88%E7%94%A8%E5%B4%87%E7%A6%8E%E5%BD%B1%E5%B0%84%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-095844515.html</a>"},{"pid":"d8ed10bda66fef90fc3a6419e171fa89a70e2bcb","tid":1876039,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T07:01:06.000Z","msg":"癲撚左"},{"pid":"d391118225886a922a1eb2c509936ab43af4a0f2","tid":1876039,"uid":314531,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T07:02:18.000Z","msg":"記得佢講香港人是狗"},{"pid":"7f638ffbc96a980b43b3913a45a5ae44a54fe14f","tid":1876039,"uid":187493,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T07:03:29.000Z","msg":"好撚記得條撚樣之前話香港人係狗<br />\n做乜而家咬自己主人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258b26dda392a99c5ffa921f9bc08666cfec7c9f","tid":1876039,"uid":278038,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"